{"tid":1538592,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[警告] 四方閪你條閪婆咪撚同班白鴿友組大台同政府傾！！！！","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:23:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T10:51:01.000Z","uid":13388,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3bd2500f6b603ff418a9d7bdc39026fff94420b5","tid":1538592,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:23:38.000Z","msg":"話說我朝朝都睇Now既時事全方位<br />\n今日就搵左四方閪你條閪婆上黎鳩UP<br />\n個觀眾林生 你On9 都算<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n四方閪你條閪婆 扮撚曬正義想同政府傾<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想重溫四方閪 既片係度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361573&amp;catCode=124&amp;topicId=566\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361573%26catCode%3D124%26topicId%3D566&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq%2B6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=d734cb37\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D361573%26catCode%3D124%26topicId%3D566&h=499674c8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=361573&amp;catCode=124&amp;topicId=566</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">話你知呀你條閪婆 全港市民個訴求好清楚<br />\n你咁做係咪對義士係condom！！！<br />\n係咪對所有香港係condom！！！<br />\n屌你老母 日日想做大台<br />\n你個白頭佬已經唔撚化架啦<br />\n你仲係咁<br />\n重新一次<br />\n今次無大台<br />\n唔好代表市民去傾<br />\n<br />\n你同班白鴿友組大台同政府傾既話<br />\n我地香港市民會拆鳩你個大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋你地D辦事處都會無啦啦仆曬街<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ut4w53G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fut4w53G.png&h=46aa4368&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/43YFeW1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F43YFeW1.png&h=d75ff5d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gUPUjoP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgUPUjoP.jpg&h=8da01733&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b23d69a83ce55ce6ddb7a1f3cd3df62984f78841","tid":1538592,"uid":13388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:26:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d98e544236a7bd3863afda7e2b75882679092fb5","tid":1538592,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:26:30.000Z","msg":"香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承諾，一世都唔原諒香港警察！<br />\n香港人，許下承